# residual-learning-for-matconvnet This is a implementation of residual learning (http://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385) in matconvnet. In this implementation, we presented 20/110 layers residual nets. We got 8.82% test error in CIFAR-10, and it was very close to 8.75% test error in original paper. ![Training and Test error curve](http://i.imgur.com/xZbQAs1.png) Usage: 1. Please install my modification of matconvnet
https://github.com/JiaRenChang/Batch_Normalized_Maxout_NIN
2. Download those files and replace. 3. run cnn_cifar.m
